column1: Many entries with "calm" entered as wind value, entered as "wind legibility". Replaces misentered value with "calm" in wind column at 8:30 a.m. on 7/24/2023
There are many instances where different hi_wc_n values are used for the same hi_wc value.
The slash is included in entries with the person value of "Arnold/west." "Arnold" and "West" are also separate person values that appear later on 7/25/2023..
Important to note that there may be different Hernandezes who all sign with the name "Hernandez" because the handwriting changes sometimes on the same page.
